From: "suricata.lu" <suricata.lu@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Apr 2026 14:09:20 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] imx8mp_evk: Port ECU-150v2 board support to U-Boot 2025.04

- defconfig: disable TCPC/Video, simplify BOOTCOMMAND, add SYSINFO/SMBIOS
- header: ECU DRAM layout (4GB default), EEPROM MAC defines
- env: uEnv.txt support, emmcboot, fatload->load, remove jh_clk
- board code: GPIO board ID, power-on sequence, EEPROM MAC in board_late_init
- DTS: strip EVK peripherals (HDMI/audio/PCIe/DSP), keep ECU hw only
- DTSI: strip display nodes, ECU USB host mode, model ECU150V2

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [embedded board port]
